182 enhancement for its bonds, including letters of credit,
183 guaranties, policies of insurance, and the like.
184 (7) As security for the payment of the principal of and
185 interest on any financing loan made to a state charter
186 educational institution, to take a pledge of and security
187 interest in:
188 a. State monies;
189 b. Federal monies;
190 c. Local funds;
191 d. Mortgage pledge of facilities; or
192 e. Any other monies or revenues received by such state
193 charter educational institution.
